name: Hello World No.13 (Christmas)
description:
"Hello World" series  Christmas special editions. The video is composed of images generated by algorithms, 1500 x 1500 pixels, single channel, color, 12/12 version.

The program related to the "Hello World" string is usually the most basic demonstration of each programming language and the first program in each programming language. The string is also the first greeting of the new AI to mankind in the future.
